commit.message:
s390.md ("*movdi_64"): Fix op_type attribute.

	* config/s390/s390.md ("*movdi_64"): Fix op_type attribute.
	("*movdf_64"): Likewise.
	("*lshrdi3_64"): Likewise.
	("blockage"): Add length attribute.
	("lit"): Likewise.

From-SVN: r58422

+	("*movdf_64"): Likewise.
+	("*lshrdi3_64"): Likewise.
+	("blockage"): Add length attribute.
+	("lit"): Likewise.
